slike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T06:48:02.000Z","msg":"早前話佢已移民美國<br />\n美國人何故對中國事說三道四？"},{"pid":"1767d6b0f45718f39380f2596ff0d214a8bebead","tid":693010,"uid":90704,"like":0,"dislike":19,"score":-19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T06:48:31.000Z","msg":"同佢一樣 比高智商香港人點醒<br />\n當年班學生同市民係好撚暴力 死幾個老解<br />\n依據呢個標準 絕對係暴動<br />\n係香港人口中搞亂北京 <br />\n當年全香港走出黎支持學運<br />\n即係叫班學生去死<br />\n全港咩演藝界乜界物界做鍵盤戰士叫北京學生去死喎<br />\n比著今日叫咩呀？ 煽動暴亂呀<br />\n<br />\n以前我人云亦云支持學生<br />\n今日比咁有智慧港人點醒 迷途知返<br />\n想係度勸大家唔好支持暴徒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ad80e92f5c5a83ee53ca2cd1c608247c8e0216a","tid":693010,"uid":34189,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0c6eb3ad3bd70b18cdf52847686bb6f810e589e6","tid":693010,"uid":11703,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T06:40:07.000Z","msg":"Book已Mark<br />\n第日佢部署移民澳洲/美國<br />\n配合日後嘅人權法案<br />\n一齊寄去領事館質疑佢有機會做間碟"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T07:01:34.000Z","msg":"晨早做左美國人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12396662530f94e886493202723c8a46b97942e5","tid":693010,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T07:12:30.000Z","msg":"鄰國咁繁榮昌盛點解唔返上去住 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26009788cd2a9464531f3fc1e86c6a140b726590","tid":693010,"uid":28765,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T07:15:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://wordpress.dr2.tw/wp-content/uploads/2014/07/%E5%B0%9A%E6%9B%B8%E5%A4%A7%E4%BA%BA%E7%9C%9F%E6%A9%9F%E9%9D%88.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwordpress.dr2.tw%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2014%2F07%2F%25E5%25B0%259A%25E6%259B%25B8%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%259C%259F%25E6%25A9%259F%25E9%259D%2588.jpg&h=f7689eba&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0bf7508e62fb1307e711cef5377c8804e53619be","tid":693010,"uid":156253,"